                    <span>Rogers is a very nice guy, and a real success. I have talked to him and read his books - wish I had his life! 
<br />
<br />Beware of jealous reviewers on Amazon - like one of the ones above (e.g. how can he have a pseudo-bike when there are photos of him with it all around the world. Also,  a website detailing his latest adventure driving around the world - people who have been to the places he went to see the authenticity in his comments on the places - and of course the photos).
<br />
<br />The book gives you a great background on commodities trading, and is well written. It cant give you trading signals as the markets change daily, though it is a great primer.
<br />
<br />So what if he isnt as rich as Soros (who he started with)! He is more successful in many areas of life than 99.99999% of people, and a great guy.
